{"product_id":"himalayan-serenity-machhapuchhre-devotional-3-piece-set","title":"Himalayan Serenity Machhapuchhre | Artistic Painting Effect | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"742\"\u003eBring the silence of the Himalayas into your space with this Machhapuchhre (Fishtail Peak) 3-Panel Split Wall Art, inspired by the sacred mountains of the Annapurna range.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"744\" data-end=\"941\"\u003eFeaturing soft dreamy blue skies, gentle golden sunrise highlights, and prayer flags flowing across the foreground, this artwork captures the calm strength and spiritual stillness of the Himalayas.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"943\" data-end=\"1176\"\u003eThe split-panel layout adds a modern aesthetic touch while maintaining the serene devotional mood of the mountain landscape. Perfect for desk setups, workspaces, meditation corners, or minimal interiors seeking depth and tranquility.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1181\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1206\"\u003eWhat You’ll Receive\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1208\" data-end=\"1342\"\u003e• 1 Set = 3 Split Panels\u003cbr data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1235\"\u003e• Matte, high-detail mountain print\u003cbr data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1273\"\u003e• Soft atmospheric color grading\u003cbr data-start=\"1305\" data-end=\"1308\"\u003e• Calm, premium aesthetic finish\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1344\" data-end=\"1347\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1374\"\u003eSize \u0026amp; Finishing Note\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1376\" data-end=\"1530\"\u003eWe print on full sheets and manually trim white borders for a clean edge-to-edge finish.\u003cbr data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1467\"\u003eFinal dimensions may vary slightly (±0.5 inch) due to trimming.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1532\" data-end=\"1535\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1537\" data-end=\"1558\"\u003eInstallation Note\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1560\" data-end=\"1670\"\u003eFrames and wall tapes are not included.\u003cbr data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1602\"\u003eYou may add our wall-stick option at checkout for easy installation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1672\" data-end=\"1675\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1677\" data-end=\"1692\"\u003ePerfect For\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1827\"\u003e• Desk setups\u003cbr data-start=\"1707\" data-end=\"1710\"\u003e• Meditation rooms\u003cbr data-start=\"1728\" data-end=\"1731\"\u003e• Living room feature walls\u003cbr data-start=\"1758\" data-end=\"1761\"\u003e• Mountain lovers\u003cbr data-start=\"1778\" data-end=\"1781\"\u003e• Spiritual interiors\u003cbr data-start=\"1802\" data-end=\"1805\"\u003e• Minimal workspaces\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51427344941352,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51427344974120,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51427345006888,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/HimalayanSerenityMachhapuchhreDevotional3PieceSet_1.webp?v=1770966957","url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/products\/himalayan-serenity-machhapuchhre-devotional-3-piece-set","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}